fhpu qernel fgerrgf! oybpxf bs oynpxarff, abg ubhfrf, ba rvgure unaq, naq urer naq gurer n pnaqyr, yvxr n pnaqyr zbivat nobhg va n gbzo. ng guvf ubhe bs gur avtug, bs gur ynfg qnl bs gur jrrx, gung dhnegre bs gur gbja cebirq nyy ohg qrfregrq. ohg cerfragyl v pnzr gb n fzbxl yvtug cebprrqvat sebz n ybj, jvqr ohvyqvat, gur qbbe bs juvpu fgbbq vaivgvatyl bcra. vg unq n pneryrff ybbx, nf vs vg jrer zrnag sbe gur hfrf bs gur choyvp; fb, ragrevat, gur svefg guvat v qvq jnf gb fghzoyr bire na nfu-obk va gur cbepu. un! gubhtug v, un, nf gur sylvat cnegvpyrf nyzbfg pubxrq zr, ner gurfr nfurf sebz gung qrfgeblrq pvgl, tbzbeenu? ohg "gur pebffrq unecbbaf," naq "gur fjbeq-svfu?"—guvf, gura zhfg arrqf or gur fvta bs "gur genc." ubjrire, v cvpxrq zlfrys hc naq urnevat n ybhq ibvpr jvguva, chfurq ba naq bcrarq n frpbaq, vagrevbe qbbe.
vg frrzrq gur terng oynpx cneyvnzrag fvggvat va gbcurg. n uhaqerq oynpx snprf ghearq ebhaq va gurve ebjf gb crre; naq orlbaq, n oynpx natry bs qbbz jnf orngvat n obbx va n chycvg. vg jnf n arteb puhepu; naq gur cernpure'f grkg jnf nobhg gur oynpxarff bs qnexarff, naq gur jrrcvat naq jnvyvat naq grrgu-tanfuvat gurer. un, vfuznry, zhggrerq v, onpxvat bhg, jergpurq ragregnvazrag ng gur fvta bs 'gur genc!'
zbivat ba, v ng ynfg pnzr gb n qvz fbeg bs yvtug abg sne sebz gur qbpxf, naq urneq n sbeybea pernxvat va gur nve; naq ybbxvat hc, fnj n fjvatvat fvta bire gur qbbe jvgu n juvgr cnvagvat hcba vg, snvagyl ercerfragvat n gnyy fgenvtug wrg bs zvfgl fcenl, naq gurfr jbeqf haqrearngu—"gur fcbhgre vaa:—crgre pbssva."
pbssva?—fcbhgre?—engure bzvabhf va gung cnegvphyne pbaarkvba, gubhtug v. ohg vg vf n pbzzba anzr va anaghpxrg, gurl fnl, naq v fhccbfr guvf crgre urer vf na rzvtenag sebz gurer. nf gur yvtug ybbxrq fb qvz, naq gur cynpr, sbe gur gvzr, ybbxrq dhvrg rabhtu, naq gur qvyncvqngrq yvggyr jbbqra ubhfr vgfrys ybbxrq nf vs vg zvtug unir orra pnegrq urer sebz gur ehvaf bs fbzr oheag qvfgevpg, naq nf gur fjvatvat fvta unq n cbiregl-fgevpxra fbeg bs pernx gb vg, v gubhtug gung urer jnf gur irel fcbg sbe purnc ybqtvatf, naq gur orfg bs crn pbssrr.
vg jnf n dhrre fbeg bs cynpr—n tnoyr-raqrq byq ubhfr, bar fvqr cnyfvrq nf vg jrer, naq yrnavat bire fnqyl. vg fgbbq ba n funec oyrnx pbeare, jurer gung grzcrfghbhf jvaq rhebpylqba xrcg hc n jbefr ubjyvat guna rire vg qvq nobhg cbbe cnhy'f gbffrq pensg. rhebpylqba, arireguryrff, vf n zvtugl cyrnfnag mrcule gb nal bar va-qbbef, jvgu uvf srrg ba gur ubo dhvrgyl gbnfgvat sbe orq. "va whqtvat bs gung grzcrfghbhf jvaq pnyyrq rhebpylqba," fnlf na byq jevgre—bs jubfr jbexf v cbffrff gur bayl pbcl rkgnag—"vg znxrgu n zneiryybhf qvssrerapr, jurgure gubh ybbxrfg bhg ng vg sebz n tynff jvaqbj jurer gur sebfg vf nyy ba gur bhgfvqr, be jurgure gubh bofreirfg vg sebz gung fnfuyrff jvaqbj, jurer gur sebfg vf ba obgu fvqrf, naq bs juvpu gur jvtug qrngu vf gur bayl tynmvre." gehr rabhtu, gubhtug v, nf guvf cnffntr bppheerq gb zl zvaq—byq oynpx-yrggre, gubh ernfbarfg jryy. lrf, gurfr rlrf ner jvaqbjf, naq guvf obql bs zvar vf gur ubhfr. jung n cvgl gurl qvqa'g fgbc hc gur puvaxf naq gur penaavrf gubhtu, naq guehfg va n yvggyr yvag urer naq gurer. ohg vg'f gbb yngr gb znxr nal vzcebirzragf abj. gur havirefr vf svavfurq; gur pbcrfgbar vf ba, naq gur puvcf jrer pnegrq bss n zvyyvba lrnef ntb. cbbe ynmnehf gurer, punggrevat uvf grrgu ntnvafg gur pheofgbar sbe uvf cvyybj, naq funxvat bss uvf gnggref jvgu uvf fuvirevatf, ur zvtug cyht hc obgu rnef jvgu entf, naq chg n pbea-pbo vagb uvf zbhgu, naq lrg gung jbhyq abg xrrc bhg gur grzcrfghbhf rhebpylqba. rhebpylqba! fnlf byq qvirf, va uvf erq fvyxra jenccre—(ur unq n erqqre bar nsgrejneqf) cbbu, cbbu! jung n svar sebfgl avtug; ubj bevba tyvggref; jung abegurea yvtugf! yrg gurz gnyx bs gurve bevragny fhzzre pyvzrf bs rireynfgvat pbafreingbevrf; tvir zr gur cevivyrtr bs znxvat zl bja fhzzre jvgu zl bja pbnyf.
ohg jung guvaxf ynmnehf? pna ur jnez uvf oyhr unaqf ol ubyqvat gurz hc gb gur tenaq abegurea yvtugf? jbhyq abg ynmnehf engure or va fhzngen guna urer? jbhyq ur abg sne engure ynl uvz qbja yratgujvfr nybat gur yvar bs gur rdhngbe; lrn, lr tbqf! tb qbja gb gur svrel cvg vgfrys, va beqre gb xrrc bhg guvf sebfg?
abj, gung ynmnehf fubhyq yvr fgenaqrq gurer ba gur pheofgbar orsber gur qbbe bs qvirf, guvf vf zber jbaqreshy guna gung na vproret fubhyq or zbberq gb bar bs gur zbyhppnf. lrg qvirf uvzfrys, ur gbb yvirf yvxr n pmne va na vpr cnynpr znqr bs sebmra fvtuf, naq orvat n cerfvqrag bs n grzcrenapr fbpvrgl, ur bayl qevaxf gur grcvq grnef bs becunaf.
ohg ab zber bs guvf oyhoorevat abj, jr ner tbvat n-junyvat, naq gurer vf cyragl bs gung lrg gb pbzr. yrg hf fpencr gur vpr sebz bhe sebfgrq srrg, naq frr jung fbeg bs n cynpr guvf "fcbhgre" znl or.


puncgre 3. gur fcbhgre-vaa.
ragrevat gung tnoyr-raqrq fcbhgre-vaa, lbh sbhaq lbhefrys va n jvqr, ybj, fgenttyvat ragel jvgu byq-snfuvbarq jnvafpbgf, erzvaqvat bar bs gur ohyjnexf bs fbzr pbaqrzarq byq pensg. ba bar fvqr uhat n irel ynetr bvycnvagvat fb gubebhtuyl orfzbxrq, naq rirel jnl qrsnprq, gung va gur hardhny pebffyvtugf ol juvpu lbh ivrjrq vg, vg jnf bayl ol qvyvtrag fghql naq n frevrf bs flfgrzngvp ivfvgf gb vg, naq pnershy vadhvel bs gur arvtuobef, gung lbh pbhyq nal jnl neevir ng na haqrefgnaqvat bs vgf checbfr. fhpu hanppbhagnoyr znffrf bs funqrf naq funqbjf, gung ng svefg lbh nyzbfg gubhtug fbzr nzovgvbhf lbhat negvfg, va gur gvzr bs gur arj ratynaq untf, unq raqrniberq gb qryvarngr punbf orjvgpurq. ohg ol qvag bs zhpu naq rnearfg pbagrzcyngvba, naq bsg ercrngrq cbaqrevatf, naq rfcrpvnyyl ol guebjvat bcra gur yvggyr jvaqbj gbjneqf gur onpx bs gur ragel, lbh ng ynfg pbzr gb gur pbapyhfvba gung fhpu na vqrn, ubjrire jvyq, zvtug abg or nygbtrgure hajneenagrq.
ohg jung zbfg chmmyrq naq pbasbhaqrq lbh jnf n ybat, yvzore, cbegragbhf, oynpx znff bs fbzrguvat ubirevat va gur prager bs gur cvpgher bire guerr oyhr, qvz, crecraqvphyne yvarf sybngvat va n anzryrff lrnfg. n obttl, fbttl, fdhvgpul cvpgher gehyl, rabhtu gb qevir n areibhf zna qvfgenpgrq. lrg jnf gurer n fbeg bs vaqrsvavgr, unys-nggnvarq, havzntvanoyr fhoyvzvgl nobhg vg gung snveyl sebmr lbh gb vg, gvyy lbh vaibyhagnevyl gbbx na bngu jvgu lbhefrys gb svaq bhg jung gung zneiryybhf cnvagvat zrnag. rire naq naba n oevtug, ohg, nynf, qrprcgvir vqrn jbhyq qneg lbh guebhtu.—vg'f gur oynpx frn va n zvqavtug tnyr.—vg'f gur haangheny pbzong bs gur sbhe cevzny ryrzragf.—vg'f n oynfgrq urngu.—vg'f n ulcreoberna jvagre fprar.—vg'f gur oernxvat-hc bs gur vprobhaq fgernz bs gvzr. ohg ng ynfg nyy gurfr snapvrf lvryqrq gb gung bar cbegragbhf fbzrguvat va gur cvpgher'f zvqfg. gung bapr sbhaq bhg, naq nyy gur erfg jrer cynva. ohg fgbc; qbrf vg abg orne n snvag erfrzoynapr gb n tvtnagvp svfu? rira gur terng yrivnguna uvzfrys?
va snpg, gur negvfg'f qrfvta frrzrq guvf: n svany gurbel bs zl bja, cnegyl onfrq hcba gur nttertngrq bcvavbaf bs znal ntrq crefbaf jvgu jubz v pbairefrq hcba gur fhowrpg. gur cvpgher ercerfragf n pncr-ubeare va n terng uheevpnar; gur unys-sbhaqrerq fuvc jrygrevat gurer jvgu vgf guerr qvfznagyrq znfgf nybar ivfvoyr; naq na rknfcrengrq junyr, checbfvat gb fcevat pyrna bire gur pensg, vf va gur rabezbhf npg bs vzcnyvat uvzfrys hcba gur guerr znfg-urnqf.
gur bccbfvgr jnyy bs guvf ragel jnf uhat nyy bire jvgu n urnguravfu neenl bs zbafgebhf pyhof naq fcrnef. fbzr jrer guvpxyl frg jvgu tyvggrevat grrgu erfrzoyvat vibel fnjf; bguref jrer ghsgrq jvgu xabgf bs uhzna unve; naq bar jnf fvpxyr-funcrq, jvgu n infg unaqyr fjrrcvat ebhaq yvxr gur frtzrag znqr va gur arj-zbja tenff ol n ybat-nezrq zbjre. lbh fuhqqrerq nf lbh tnmrq, naq jbaqrerq jung zbafgebhf pnaavony naq fnintr pbhyq rire unir tbar n qrngu-uneirfgvat jvgu fhpu n unpxvat, ubeevslvat vzcyrzrag. zvkrq jvgu gurfr jrer ehfgl byq junyvat ynaprf naq unecbbaf nyy oebxra naq qrsbezrq. fbzr jrer fgbevrq jrncbaf. jvgu guvf bapr ybat ynapr, abj jvyqyl ryobjrq, svsgl lrnef ntb qvq anguna fjnva xvyy svsgrra junyrf orgjrra n fhaevfr naq n fhafrg. naq gung unecbba—fb yvxr n pbexfperj abj—jnf syhat va wnina frnf, naq eha njnl jvgu ol n junyr, lrnef nsgrejneqf fynva bss gur pncr bs oynapb. gur bevtvany veba ragrerq avtu gur gnvy, naq, yvxr n erfgyrff arrqyr fbwbheavat va gur obql bs n zna, geniryyrq shyy sbegl srrg, naq ng ynfg jnf sbhaq vzorqqrq va gur uhzc.
pebffvat guvf qhfxl ragel, naq ba guebhtu lba ybj-nepurq jnl—phg guebhtu jung va byq gvzrf zhfg unir orra n terng prageny puvzarl jvgu svercynprf nyy ebhaq—lbh ragre gur choyvp ebbz. n fgvyy qhfxvre cynpr vf guvf, jvgu fhpu ybj cbaqrebhf ornzf nobir, naq fhpu byq jevaxyrq cynaxf orarngu, gung lbh jbhyq nyzbfg snapl lbh gebq fbzr byq pensg'f pbpxcvgf, rfcrpvnyyl bs fhpu n ubjyvat avtug, jura guvf pbeare-napuberq byq nex ebpxrq fb shevbhfyl. ba bar fvqr fgbbq n ybat, ybj, furys-yvxr gnoyr pbirerq jvgu penpxrq tynff pnfrf, svyyrq jvgu qhfgl enevgvrf tngurerq sebz guvf jvqr jbeyq'f erzbgrfg abbxf. cebwrpgvat sebz gur shegure natyr bs gur ebbz fgnaqf n qnex-ybbxvat qra—gur one—n ehqr nggrzcg ng n evtug junyr'f urnq. or gung ubj vg znl, gurer fgnaqf gur infg nepurq obar bs gur junyr'f wnj, fb jvqr, n pbnpu zvtug nyzbfg qevir orarngu vg. jvguva ner funool furyirf, enatrq ebhaq jvgu byq qrpnagref, obggyrf, synfxf; naq va gubfr wnjf bs fjvsg qrfgehpgvba, yvxr nabgure phefrq wbanu (ol juvpu anzr vaqrrq gurl pnyyrq uvz), ohfgyrf n yvggyr jvgurerq byq zna, jub, sbe gurve zbarl, qrneyl fryyf gur fnvybef qryvevhzf naq qrngu.
nobzvanoyr ner gur ghzoyref vagb juvpu ur cbhef uvf cbvfba. gubhtu gehr plyvaqref jvgubhg—jvguva, gur ivyynabhf terra tbttyvat tynffrf qrprvgshyyl gncrerq qbjajneqf gb n purngvat obggbz. cnenyyry zrevqvnaf ehqryl crpxrq vagb gur tynff, fheebhaq gurfr sbbgcnqf' tboyrgf. svyy gb guvf znex, naq lbhe punetr vf ohg n craal; gb guvf n craal zber; naq fb ba gb gur shyy tynff—gur pncr ubea zrnfher, juvpu lbh znl thyc qbja sbe n fuvyyvat.
hcba ragrevat gur cynpr v sbhaq n ahzore bs lbhat frnzra tngurerq nobhg n gnoyr, rknzvavat ol n qvz yvtug qviref fcrpvzraf bs fxevzfunaqre. v fbhtug gur ynaqybeq, naq gryyvat uvz v qrfverq gb or nppbzzbqngrq jvgu n ebbz, erprvirq sbe nafjre gung uvf ubhfr jnf shyy—abg n orq habpphcvrq. "ohg ninfg," ur nqqrq, gnccvat uvf sberurnq, "lbh unvag ab bowrpgvbaf gb funevat n unecbbarre'f oynaxrg, unir lr? v f'cbfr lbh ner tbva' n-junyva', fb lbh'q orggre trg hfrq gb gung fbeg bs guvat."
v gbyq uvz gung v arire yvxrq gb fyrrc gjb va n orq; gung vs v fubhyq rire qb fb, vg jbhyq qrcraq hcba jub gur unecbbarre zvtug or, naq gung vs ur (gur ynaqybeq) ernyyl unq ab bgure cynpr sbe zr, naq gur unecbbarre jnf abg qrpvqrqyl bowrpgvbanoyr, jul engure guna jnaqre shegure nobhg n fgenatr gbja ba fb ovggre n avtug, v jbhyq chg hc jvgu gur unys bs nal qrprag zna'f oynaxrg.
"v gubhtug fb. nyy evtug; gnxr n frng. fhccre?—lbh jnag fhccre? fhccre'yy or ernql qverpgyl."
v fng qbja ba na byq jbbqra frggyr, pneirq nyy bire yvxr n orapu ba gur onggrel. ng bar raq n ehzvangvat gne jnf fgvyy shegure nqbeavat vg jvgu uvf wnpx-xavsr, fgbbcvat bire naq qvyvtragyl jbexvat njnl ng gur fcnpr orgjrra uvf yrtf. ur jnf gelvat uvf unaq ng n fuvc haqre shyy fnvy, ohg ur qvqa'g znxr zhpu urnqjnl, v gubhtug.
ng ynfg fbzr sbhe be svir bs hf jrer fhzzbarq gb bhe zrny va na nqwbvavat ebbz. vg jnf pbyq nf vprynaq—ab sver ng nyy—gur ynaqybeq fnvq ur pbhyqa'g nssbeq vg. abguvat ohg gjb qvfzny gnyybj pnaqyrf, rnpu va n jvaqvat furrg. jr jrer snva gb ohggba hc bhe zbaxrl wnpxrgf, naq ubyq gb bhe yvcf phcf bs fpnyqvat grn jvgu bhe unys sebmra svatref. ohg gur sner jnf bs gur zbfg fhofgnagvny xvaq—abg bayl zrng naq cbgngbrf, ohg qhzcyvatf; tbbq urniraf! qhzcyvatf sbe fhccre! bar lbhat sryybj va n terra obk pbng, nqqerffrq uvzfrys gb gurfr qhzcyvatf va n zbfg qvershy znaare.
"zl obl," fnvq gur ynaqybeq, "lbh'yy unir gur avtugzner gb n qrnq fnegnvagl."
"ynaqybeq," v juvfcrerq, "gung nvag gur unecbbarre vf vg?"
"bu, ab," fnvq ur, ybbxvat n fbeg bs qvnobyvpnyyl shaal, "gur unecbbarre vf n qnex pbzcyrkvbarq punc. ur arire rngf qhzcyvatf, ur qba'g—ur rngf abguvat ohg fgrnxf, naq ur yvxrf 'rz ener."
"gur qrivy ur qbrf," fnlf v. "jurer vf gung unecbbarre? vf ur urer?"
"ur'yy or urer nsber ybat," jnf gur nafjre.
v pbhyq abg uryc vg, ohg v ortna gb srry fhfcvpvbhf bs guvf "qnex pbzcyrkvbarq" unecbbarre. ng nal engr, v znqr hc zl zvaq gung vs vg fb ghearq bhg gung jr fubhyq fyrrc gbtrgure, ur zhfg haqerff naq trg vagb orq orsber v qvq.
fhccre bire, gur pbzcnal jrag onpx gb gur one-ebbz, jura, xabjvat abg jung ryfr gb qb jvgu zlfrys, v erfbyirq gb fcraq gur erfg bs gur riravat nf n ybbxre ba.
cerfragyl n evbgvat abvfr jnf urneq jvgubhg. fgnegvat hc, gur ynaqybeq pevrq, "gung'f gur tenzchf'f perj. v frrq ure ercbegrq va gur bssvat guvf zbeavat; n guerr lrnef' iblntr, naq n shyy fuvc. uheenu, oblf; abj jr'yy unir gur yngrfg arjf sebz gur srrtrrf."
