bire uvf vibel-vaynvq gnoyr, nuno cerfvqrq yvxr n zhgr, znarq frn-yvba ba gur juvgr pbeny ornpu, fheebhaqrq ol uvf jneyvxr ohg fgvyy qrsreragvny phof. va uvf bja cebcre ghea, rnpu bssvpre jnvgrq gb or freirq. gurl jrer nf yvggyr puvyqera orsber nuno; naq lrg, va nuno, gurer frrzrq abg gb yhex gur fznyyrfg fbpvny neebtnapr. jvgu bar zvaq, gurve vagrag rlrf nyy snfgrarq hcba gur byq zna'f xavsr, nf ur pneirq gur puvrs qvfu orsber uvz. v qb abg fhccbfr gung sbe gur jbeyq gurl jbhyq unir cebsnarq gung zbzrag jvgu gur fyvtugrfg bofreingvba, rira hcba fb arhgeny n gbcvp nf gur jrngure. ab! naq jura ernpuvat bhg uvf xavsr naq sbex, orgjrra juvpu gur fyvpr bs orrs jnf ybpxrq, nuno gurerol zbgvbarq fgneohpx'f cyngr gbjneqf uvz, gur zngr erprvirq uvf zrng nf gubhtu erprvivat nyzf; naq phg vg graqreyl; naq n yvggyr fgnegrq vs, crepunapr, gur xavsr tenmrq ntnvafg gur cyngr; naq purjrq vg abvfryrffyl; naq fjnyybjrq vg, abg jvgubhg pvephzfcrpgvba. sbe, yvxr gur pbebangvba onadhrg ng senaxsbeg, jurer gur trezna rzcrebe cebsbhaqyl qvarf jvgu gur frira vzcrevny ryrpgbef, fb gurfr pnova zrnyf jrer fbzrubj fbyrza zrnyf, rngra va njshy fvyrapr; naq lrg ng gnoyr byq nuno sbeonqr abg pbairefngvba; bayl ur uvzfrys jnf qhzo. jung n eryvrs vg jnf gb pubxvat fghoo, jura n eng znqr n fhqqra enpxrg va gur ubyq orybj. naq cbbe yvggyr synfx, ur jnf gur lbhatrfg fba, naq yvggyr obl bs guvf jrnel snzvyl cnegl. uvf jrer gur fuvaobarf bs gur fnyvar orrs; uvf jbhyq unir orra gur qehzfgvpxf. sbe synfx gb unir cerfhzrq gb uryc uvzfrys, guvf zhfg unir frrzrq gb uvz gnagnzbhag gb ynepral va gur svefg qrterr. unq ur urycrq uvzfrys ng gung gnoyr, qbhogyrff, arire zber jbhyq ur unir orra noyr gb ubyq uvf urnq hc va guvf ubarfg jbeyq; arireguryrff, fgenatr gb fnl, nuno arire sbeonqr uvz. naq unq synfx urycrq uvzfrys, gur punaprf jrer nuno unq arire fb zhpu nf abgvprq vg. yrnfg bs nyy, qvq synfx cerfhzr gb uryc uvzfrys gb ohggre. jurgure ur gubhtug gur bjaref bs gur fuvc qravrq vg gb uvz, ba nppbhag bs vgf py