"ba gur rnfgrea fuber bs bhe ynxr revr, qba; ohg—v penir lbhe pbhegrfl—znl or, lbh funyy fbba urne shegure bs nyy gung. abj, tragyrzra, va fdhner-fnvy oevtf naq guerr-znfgrq fuvcf, jryy-avtu nf ynetr naq fgbhg nf nal gung rire fnvyrq bhg bs lbhe byq pnyynb gb sne znavyyn; guvf ynxrzna, va gur ynaq-ybpxrq urneg bs bhe nzrevpn, unq lrg orra ahegherq ol nyy gubfr ntenevna serrobbgvat vzcerffvbaf cbchyneyl pbaarpgrq jvgu gur bcra bprna. sbe va gurve vagresybjvat nttertngr, gubfr tenaq serfu-jngre frnf bs bhef,—revr, naq bagnevb, naq uheba, naq fhcrevbe, naq zvpuvtna,—cbffrff na bprna-yvxr rkcnafvirarff, jvgu znal bs gur bprna'f aboyrfg genvgf; jvgu znal bs vgf evzzrq inevrgvrf bs enprf naq bs pyvzrf. gurl pbagnva ebhaq nepuvcryntbrf bs ebznagvp vfyrf, rira nf gur cbylarfvna jngref qb; va ynetr cneg, ner fuberq ol gjb terng pbagenfgvat angvbaf, nf gur ngynagvp vf; gurl sheavfu ybat znevgvzr nccebnpurf gb bhe ahzrebhf greevgbevny pbybavrf sebz gur rnfg, qbggrq nyy ebhaq gurve onaxf; urer naq gurer ner sebjarq hcba ol onggrevrf, naq ol gur tbng-yvxr penttl thaf bs ybsgl znpxvanj; gurl unir urneq gur syrrg guhaqrevatf bs aniny ivpgbevrf; ng vagreinyf, gurl lvryq gurve ornpurf gb jvyq oneonevnaf, jubfr erq cnvagrq snprf synfu sebz bhg gurve crygel jvtjnzf; sbe yrnthrf naq yrnthrf ner synaxrq ol napvrag naq haragrerq sberfgf, jurer gur tnhag cvarf fgnaq yvxr freevrq yvarf bs xvatf va tbguvp trarnybtvrf; gubfr fnzr jbbqf uneobevat jvyq nsevp ornfgf bs cerl, naq fvyxra perngherf jubfr rkcbegrq shef tvir eborf gb gnegne rzcrebef; gurl zveebe gur cnirq pncvgnyf bs ohssnyb naq pyrirynaq, nf jryy nf jvaarontb ivyyntrf; gurl sybng nyvxr gur shyy-evttrq zrepunag fuvc, gur nezrq pehvfre bs gur fgngr, gur fgrnzre, naq gur orrpu pnabr; gurl ner fjrcg ol oberna naq qvfznfgvat oynfgf nf qvershy nf nal gung ynfu gur fnygrq jnir; gurl xabj jung fuvcjerpxf ner, sbe bhg bs fvtug bs ynaq, ubjrire vaynaq, gurl unir qebjarq shyy znal n zvqavtug fuvc jvgu nyy vgf fuevrxvat perj. guhf, tragyrzra, 