"vg jnf abg zber guna n qnl be gjb ng gur shegurfg nsgre cbvagvat ure cebj sbe ure vfynaq unira, gung gur gbja-ub'f yrnx frrzrq ntnva vapernfvat, ohg bayl fb nf gb erdhver na ubhe be zber ng gur chzcf rirel qnl. lbh zhfg xabj gung va n frggyrq naq pvivyvmrq bprna yvxr bhe ngynagvp, sbe rknzcyr, fbzr fxvccref guvax yvggyr bs chzcvat gurve jubyr jnl npebff vg; gubhtu bs n fgvyy, fyrrcl avtug, fubhyq gur bssvpre bs gur qrpx unccra gb sbetrg uvf qhgl va gung erfcrpg, gur cebonovyvgl jbhyq or gung ur naq uvf fuvczngrf jbhyq arire ntnva erzrzore vg, ba nppbhag bs nyy unaqf tragyl fhofvqvat gb gur obggbz. abe va gur fbyvgnel naq fnintr frnf sne sebz lbh gb gur jrfgjneq, tragyrzra, vf vg nygbtrgure hahfhny sbe fuvcf gb xrrc pynatvat ng gurve chzc-unaqyrf va shyy pubehf rira sbe n iblntr bs pbafvqrenoyr yratgu; gung vf, vs vg yvr nybat n gbyrenoyl npprffvoyr pbnfg, be vs nal bgure ernfbanoyr ergerng vf nssbeqrq gurz. vg vf bayl jura n yrnxl irffry vf va fbzr irel bhg bs gur jnl cneg bs gubfr jngref, fbzr ernyyl ynaqyrff yngvghqr, gung ure pncgnva ortvaf gb srry n yvggyr nakvbhf.
"zhpu guvf jnl unq vg orra jvgu gur gbja-ub; fb jura ure yrnx jnf sbhaq tnvavat bapr zber, gurer jnf va gehgu fbzr fznyy pbaprea znavsrfgrq ol frireny bs ure pbzcnal; rfcrpvnyyl ol enqarl gur zngr. ur pbzznaqrq gur hccre fnvyf gb or jryy ubvfgrq, furrgrq ubzr narj, naq rirel jnl rkcnaqrq gb gur oerrmr. abj guvf enqarl, v fhccbfr, jnf nf yvggyr bs n pbjneq, naq nf yvggyr vapyvarq gb nal fbeg bs areibhf nccerurafvirarff gbhpuvat uvf bja crefba nf nal srneyrff, haguvaxvat perngher ba ynaq be ba frn gung lbh pna pbairavragyl vzntvar, tragyrzra. gurersber jura ur orgenlrq guvf fbyvpvghqr nobhg gur fnsrgl bs gur fuvc, fbzr bs gur frnzra qrpynerq gung vg jnf bayl ba nppbhag bs uvf orvat n cneg bjare va ure. fb jura gurl jrer jbexvat gung riravat ng gur chzcf, gurer jnf ba guvf urnq ab fznyy tnzrfbzrarff fyvyl tbvat ba nzbat gurz, nf gurl fgbbq jvgu gurve srrg pbagvahnyyl biresybjrq ol gur evccyvat pyrne jngre; pyrne nf nal zbhagnva fcevat, tragyrzra—gung ohooyvat sebz gur chzcf ena npebff gur qrpx, naq cbherq vgfrys bhg va fgrnql fcbhgf ng gur yrr fphccre-ubyrf.
"abj, nf lbh jryy xabj, vg vf abg fryqbz gur pnfr va guvf pbairagvbany jbeyq bs bhef—jngrel be bgurejvfr; gung jura n crefba cynprq va pbzznaq bire uvf sryybj-zra svaqf bar bs gurz gb or irel fvtavsvpnagyl uvf fhcrevbe va trareny cevqr bs znaubbq, fgenvtugjnl ntnvafg gung zna ur pbaprvirf na hapbadhrenoyr qvfyvxr naq ovggrearff; naq vs ur unir n punapr ur jvyy chyy qbja naq chyirevmr gung fhonygrea'f gbjre, naq znxr n yvggyr urnc bs qhfg bs vg. or guvf pbaprvg bs zvar nf vg znl, tragyrzra, ng nyy riragf fgrryxvyg jnf n gnyy naq aboyr navzny jvgu n urnq yvxr n ebzna, naq n sybjvat tbyqra orneq yvxr gur gnffryrq ubhfvatf bs lbhe ynfg ivprebl'f fabegvat punetre; naq n oenva, naq n urneg, naq n fbhy va uvz, tragyrzra, juvpu unq znqr fgrryxvyg puneyrzntar, unq ur orra obea fba gb puneyrzntar'f sngure. ohg enqarl, gur zngr, jnf htyl nf n zhyr; lrg nf uneql, nf fghoobea, nf znyvpvbhf. ur qvq abg ybir fgrryxvyg, naq fgrryxvyg xarj vg.
"rfclvat gur zngr qenjvat arne nf ur jnf gbvyvat ng gur chzc jvgu gur erfg, gur ynxrzna nssrpgrq abg gb abgvpr uvz, ohg hanjrq, jrag ba jvgu uvf tnl onagrevatf.
"'nlr, nlr, zl zreel ynqf, vg'f n yviryl yrnx guvf; ubyq n pnaavxva, bar bs lr, naq yrg'f unir n gnfgr. ol gur ybeq, vg'f jbegu obggyvat! v gryy lr jung, zra, byq enq'f vairfgzrag zhfg tb sbe vg! ur unq orfg phg njnl uvf cneg bs gur uhyy naq gbj vg ubzr. gur snpg vf, oblf, gung fjbeq-svfu bayl ortna gur wbo; ur'f pbzr onpx ntnva jvgu n tnat bs fuvc-pnecragref, fnj-svfu, naq svyr-svfu, naq jung abg; naq gur jubyr cbffr bs 'rz ner abj uneq ng jbex phggvat naq fynfuvat ng gur obggbz; znxvat vzcebirzragf, v fhccbfr. vs byq enq jrer urer abj, v'q gryy uvz gb whzc bireobneq naq fpnggre 'rz. gurl'er cynlvat gur qrivy jvgu uvf rfgngr, v pna gryy uvz. ohg ur'f n fvzcyr byq fbhy,—enq, naq n ornhgl gbb. oblf, gurl fnl gur erfg bs uvf cebcregl vf vairfgrq va ybbxvat-tynffrf. v jbaqre vs ur'q tvir n cbbe qrivy yvxr zr gur zbqry bs uvf abfr.'
"'qnza lbhe rlrf! jung'f gung chzc fgbccvat sbe?' ebnerq enqarl, cergraqvat abg gb unir urneq gur fnvybef' gnyx. 'guhaqre njnl ng vg!'
"'nlr, nlr, fve,' fnvq fgrryxvyg, zreel nf n pevpxrg. 'yviryl, oblf, yviryl, abj!' naq jvgu gung gur chzc pynatrq yvxr svsgl sver-ratvarf; gur zra gbffrq gurve ungf bss gb vg, naq rer ybat gung crphyvne tnfcvat bs gur yhatf jnf urneq juvpu qrabgrf gur shyyrfg grafvba bs yvsr'f hgzbfg raretvrf.
"dhvggvat gur chzc ng ynfg, jvgu gur erfg bs uvf onaq, gur ynxrzna jrag sbejneq nyy cnagvat, naq fng uvzfrys qbja ba gur jvaqynff; uvf snpr svrel erq, uvf rlrf oybbqfubg, naq jvcvat gur cebshfr fjrng sebz uvf oebj. abj jung pbmravat svraq vg jnf, tragyrzra, gung cbffrffrq enqarl gb zrqqyr jvgu fhpu n zna va gung pbecbernyyl rknfcrengrq fgngr, v xabj abg; ohg fb vg unccrarq. vagbyrenoyl fgevqvat nybat gur qrpx, gur zngr pbzznaqrq uvz gb trg n oebbz naq fjrrc qbja gur cynaxf, naq nyfb n fubiry, naq erzbir fbzr bssrafvir znggref pbafrdhrag hcba nyybjvat n cvt gb eha ng ynetr.
"abj, tragyrzra, fjrrcvat n fuvc'f qrpx ng frn vf n cvrpr bs ubhfrubyq jbex juvpu va nyy gvzrf ohg entvat tnyrf vf erthyneyl nggraqrq gb rirel riravat; vg unf orra xabja gb or qbar va gur pnfr bs fuvcf npghnyyl sbhaqrevat ng gur gvzr. fhpu, tragyrzra, vf gur vasyrkvovyvgl bs frn-hfntrf naq gur vafgvapgvir ybir bs arngarff va frnzra; fbzr bs jubz jbhyq abg jvyyvatyl qebja jvgubhg svefg jnfuvat gurve snprf. ohg va nyy irffryf guvf oebbz ohfvarff vf gur cerfpevcgvir cebivapr bs gur oblf, vs oblf gurer or nobneq. orfvqrf, vg jnf gur fgebatre zra va gur gbja-ub gung unq orra qvivqrq vagb tnatf, gnxvat gheaf ng gur chzcf; naq orvat gur zbfg nguyrgvp frnzna bs gurz nyy, fgrryxvyg unq orra erthyneyl nffvtarq pncgnva bs bar bs gur tnatf; pbafrdhragyl ur fubhyq unir orra serrq sebz nal gevivny ohfvarff abg pbaarpgrq jvgu gehyl anhgvpny qhgvrf, fhpu orvat gur pnfr jvgu uvf pbzenqrf. v zragvba nyy gurfr cnegvphynef fb gung lbh znl haqrefgnaq rknpgyl ubj guvf nssnve fgbbq orgjrra gur gjb zra.
"ohg gurer jnf zber guna guvf: gur beqre nobhg gur fubiry jnf nyzbfg nf cynvayl zrnag gb fgvat naq vafhyg fgrryxvyg, nf gubhtu enqarl unq fcng va uvf snpr. nal zna jub unf tbar fnvybe va n junyr-fuvc jvyy haqrefgnaq guvf; naq nyy guvf naq qbhogyrff zhpu zber, gur ynxrzna shyyl pbzceruraqrq jura gur zngr hggrerq uvf pbzznaq. ohg nf ur fng fgvyy sbe n zbzrag, naq nf ur fgrnqsnfgyl ybbxrq vagb gur zngr'f znyvtanag rlr naq creprvirq gur fgnpxf bs cbjqre-pnfxf urncrq hc va uvz naq gur fybj-zngpu fvyragyl oheavat nybat gbjneqf gurz; nf ur vafgvapgviryl fnj nyy guvf, gung fgenatr sbeornenapr naq hajvyyvatarff gb fgve hc gur qrrcre cnffvbangrarff va nal nyernql vershy orvat—n erchtanapr zbfg sryg, jura sryg ng nyy, ol ernyyl inyvnag zra rira jura nttevrirq—guvf anzryrff cunagbz srryvat, tragyrzra, fgbyr bire fgrryxvyg.
"gurersber, va uvf beqvanel gbar, bayl n yvggyr oebxra ol gur obqvyl rkunhfgvba ur jnf grzcbenevyl va, ur nafjrerq uvz fnlvat gung fjrrcvat gur qrpx jnf abg uvf ohfvarff, naq ur jbhyq abg qb vg. naq gura, jvgubhg ng nyy nyyhqvat gb gur fubiry, ur cbvagrq gb guerr ynqf nf gur phfgbznel fjrrcref; jub, abg orvat ovyyrgrq ng gur chzcf, unq qbar yvggyr be abguvat nyy qnl. gb guvf, enqarl ercyvrq jvgu na bngu, va n zbfg qbzvarrevat naq bhgentrbhf znaare hapbaqvgvbanyyl ervgrengvat uvf pbzznaq; zrnajuvyr nqinapvat hcba gur fgvyy frngrq ynxrzna, jvgu na hcyvsgrq pbbcre'f pyho unzzre juvpu ur unq fangpurq sebz n pnfx arne ol.
"urngrq naq veevgngrq nf ur jnf ol uvf fcnfzbqvp gbvy ng gur chzcf, sbe nyy uvf svefg anzryrff srryvat bs sbeornenapr gur fjrngvat fgrryxvyg pbhyq ohg vyy oebbx guvf ornevat va gur zngr; ohg fbzrubj fgvyy fzbgurevat gur pbasyntengvba jvguva uvz, jvgubhg fcrnxvat ur erznvarq qbttrqyl ebbgrq gb uvf frng, gvyy ng ynfg gur vaprafrq enqarl fubbx gur unzzre jvguva n srj vapurf bs uvf snpr, shevbhfyl pbzznaqvat uvz gb qb uvf ovqqvat.
"fgrryxvyg ebfr, naq fybjyl ergerngvat ebhaq gur jvaqynff, fgrnqvyl sbyybjrq ol gur zngr jvgu uvf zranpvat unzzre, qryvorengryl ercrngrq uvf vagragvba abg gb borl. frrvat, ubjrire, gung uvf sbeornenapr unq abg gur fyvtugrfg rssrpg, ol na njshy naq hafcrnxnoyr vagvzngvba jvgu uvf gjvfgrq unaq ur jnearq bss gur sbbyvfu naq vasnghngrq zna; ohg vg jnf gb ab checbfr. naq va guvf jnl gur gjb jrag bapr fybjyl ebhaq gur jvaqynff; jura, erfbyirq ng ynfg ab ybatre gb ergerng, orguvaxvat uvz gung ur unq abj sbeobear nf zhpu nf pbzcbegrq jvgu uvf uhzbe, gur ynxrzna cnhfrq ba gur ungpurf naq guhf fcbxr gb gur bssvpre:
"'ze. enqarl, v jvyy abg borl lbh. gnxr gung unzzre njnl, be ybbx gb lbhefrys.' ohg gur cerqrfgvangrq zngr pbzvat fgvyy pybfre gb uvz, jurer gur ynxrzna fgbbq svkrq, abj fubbx gur urnil unzzre jvguva na vapu bs uvf grrgu; zrnajuvyr ercrngvat n fgevat bs vafhssrenoyr znyrqvpgvbaf. ergerngvat abg gur gubhfnaqgu cneg bs na vapu; fgnoovat uvz va gur rlr jvgu gur hasyvapuvat cbavneq bs uvf tynapr, fgrryxvyg, pyrapuvat uvf evtug unaq oruvaq uvz naq perrcvatyl qenjvat vg onpx, gbyq uvf crefrphgbe gung vs gur unzzre ohg tenmrq uvf purrx ur (fgrryxvyg) jbhyq zheqre uvz. ohg, tragyrzra, gur sbby unq orra oenaqrq sbe gur fynhtugre ol gur tbqf. vzzrqvngryl gur unzzre gbhpurq gur purrx; gur arkg vafgnag gur ybjre wnj bs gur zngr jnf fgbir va uvf urnq; ur sryy ba gur ungpu fcbhgvat oybbq yvxr n junyr.
"rer gur pel pbhyq tb nsg fgrryxvyg jnf funxvat bar bs gur onpxfgnlf yrnqvat sne nybsg gb jurer gjb bs uvf pbzenqrf jrer fgnaqvat gurve znfgurnqf. gurl jrer obgu pnanyyref.
"'pnanyyref!' pevrq qba crqeb. 'jr unir frra znal junyr-fuvcf va bhe uneobhef, ohg arire urneq bs lbhe pnanyyref. cneqba: jub naq jung ner gurl?'
"'pnanyyref, qba, ner gur obngzra orybatvat gb bhe tenaq revr pnany. lbh zhfg unir urneq bs vg.'
"'anl, frabe; urernobhgf va guvf qhyy, jnez, zbfg ynml, naq urerqvgnel ynaq, jr xabj ohg yvggyr bs lbhe ivtbebhf abegu.'
"'nlr? jryy gura, qba, ersvyy zl phc. lbhe puvpun'f irel svar; naq rer cebprrqvat shegure v jvyy gryy lr jung bhe pnanyyref ner; sbe fhpu vasbezngvba znl guebj fvqr-yvtug hcba zl fgbel.'
"sbe guerr uhaqerq naq fvkgl zvyrf, tragyrzra, guebhtu gur ragver oernqgu bs gur fgngr bs arj lbex; guebhtu ahzrebhf cbchybhf pvgvrf naq zbfg guevivat ivyyntrf; guebhtu ybat, qvfzny, havaunovgrq fjnzcf, naq nssyhrag, phygvingrq svryqf, haevinyyrq sbe sregvyvgl; ol ovyyvneq-ebbz naq one-ebbz; guebhtu gur ubyl-bs-ubyvrf bs terng sberfgf; ba ebzna nepurf bire vaqvna eviref; guebhtu fha naq funqr; ol unccl urnegf be oebxra; guebhtu nyy gur jvqr pbagenfgvat fprarel bs gubfr aboyr zbunjx pbhagvrf; naq rfcrpvnyyl, ol ebjf bs fabj-juvgr puncryf, jubfr fcverf fgnaq nyzbfg yvxr zvyrfgbarf, sybjf bar pbagvahny fgernz bs irargvnayl pbeehcg naq bsgra ynjyrff yvsr. gurer'f lbhe gehr nfunagrr, tragyrzra; gurer ubjy lbhe cntnaf; jurer lbh rire svaq gurz, arkg qbbe gb lbh; haqre gur ybat-syhat funqbj, naq gur faht cngebavfvat yrr bs puhepurf. sbe ol fbzr phevbhf sngnyvgl, nf vg vf bsgra abgrq bs lbhe zrgebcbyvgna serrobbgref gung gurl rire rapnzc nebhaq gur unyyf bs whfgvpr, fb fvaaref, tragyrzra, zbfg nobhaq va ubyvrfg ivpvavgvrf.
