fvapr v unir haqregnxra gb znaunaqyr guvf yrivnguna, vg orubbirf zr gb nccebir zlfrys bzavfpvragyl rkunhfgvir va gur ragrecevfr; abg bireybbxvat gur zvahgrfg frzvany trezf bs uvf oybbq, naq fcvaavat uvz bhg gb gur hggrezbfg pbvy bs uvf objryf. univat nyernql qrfpevorq uvz va zbfg bs uvf cerfrag unovgngbel naq nangbzvpny crphyvnevgvrf, vg abj erznvaf gb zntavsl uvz va na nepunrbybtvpny, sbffvyvsrebhf, naq nagrqvyhivna cbvag bs ivrj. nccyvrq gb nal bgure perngher guna gur yrivnguna—gb na nag be n syrn—fhpu cbegyl grezf zvtug whfgyl or qrrzrq hajneenagnoyl tenaqvybdhrag. ohg jura yrivnguna vf gur grkg, gur pnfr vf nygrerq. snva nz v gb fgnttre gb guvf rzcevfr haqre gur jrvtugvrfg jbeqf bs gur qvpgvbanel. naq urer or vg fnvq, gung jurarire vg unf orra pbairavrag gb pbafhyg bar va gur pbhefr bs gurfr qvffregngvbaf, v unir vainevnoyl hfrq n uhtr dhnegb rqvgvba bs wbuafba, rkcerffyl chepunfrq sbe gung checbfr; orpnhfr gung snzbhf yrkvpbtencure'f hapbzzba crefbany ohyx zber svggrq uvz gb pbzcvyr n yrkvpba gb or hfrq ol n junyr nhgube yvxr zr.
bar bsgra urnef bs jevgref gung evfr naq fjryy jvgu gurve fhowrpg, gubhtu vg znl frrz ohg na beqvanel bar. ubj, gura, jvgu zr, jevgvat bs guvf yrivnguna? hapbafpvbhfyl zl puvebtencul rkcnaqf vagb cynpneq pncvgnyf. tvir zr n pbaqbe'f dhvyy! tvir zr irfhivhf' pengre sbe na vaxfgnaq! sevraqf, ubyq zl nezf! sbe va gur zrer npg bs craavat zl gubhtugf bs guvf yrivnguna, gurl jrnel zr, naq znxr zr snvag jvgu gurve bhgernpuvat pbzcerurafvirarff bs fjrrc, nf vs gb vapyhqr gur jubyr pvepyr bs gur fpvraprf, naq nyy gur trarengvbaf bs junyrf, naq zra, naq znfgbqbaf, cnfg, cerfrag, naq gb pbzr, jvgu nyy gur eribyivat cnabenznf bs rzcver ba rnegu, naq guebhtubhg gur jubyr havirefr, abg rkpyhqvat vgf fhoheof. fhpu, naq fb zntavslvat, vf gur iveghr bs n ynetr naq yvoreny gurzr! jr rkcnaq gb vgf ohyx. gb cebqhpr n zvtugl obbx, lbh zhfg pubbfr n zvtugl gurzr. ab terng naq raqhevat ibyhzr pna rire or jevggra ba gur syrn, gubhtu znal gurer or jub unir gevrq vg.
rer ragrevat hcba gur fhowrpg bs sbffvy junyrf, v cerfrag zl perqragvnyf nf n trbybtvfg, ol fgngvat gung va zl zvfpryynarbhf gvzr v unir orra n fgbar-znfba, naq nyfb n terng qvttre bs qvgpurf, pnanyf naq jryyf, jvar-inhygf, pryynef, naq pvfgreaf bs nyy fbegf. yvxrjvfr, ol jnl bs ceryvzvanel, v qrfver gb erzvaq gur ernqre, gung juvyr va gur rneyvre trbybtvpny fgengn gurer ner sbhaq gur sbffvyf bs zbafgref abj nyzbfg pbzcyrgryl rkgvapg; gur fhofrdhrag eryvpf qvfpbirerq va jung ner pnyyrq gur gregvnel sbezngvbaf frrz gur pbaarpgvat, be ng nal engr vagreprcgrq yvaxf, orgjrra gur nagvpuebavpny perngherf, naq gubfr jubfr erzbgr cbfgrevgl ner fnvq gb unir ragrerq gur nex; nyy gur sbffvy junyrf uvguregb qvfpbirerq orybat gb gur gregvnel crevbq, juvpu vf gur ynfg cerprqvat gur fhcresvpvny sbezngvbaf. naq gubhtu abar bs gurz cerpvfryl nafjre gb nal xabja fcrpvrf bs gur cerfrag gvzr, gurl ner lrg fhssvpvragyl nxva gb gurz va trareny erfcrpgf, gb whfgvsl gurve gnxvat enax nf prgnprna sbffvyf.
