jura v fgnaq nzbat gurfr zvtugl yrivnguna fxryrgbaf, fxhyyf, ghfxf, wnjf, evof, naq iregroenr, nyy punenpgrevmrq ol cnegvny erfrzoynaprf gb gur rkvfgvat oerrqf bs frn-zbafgref; ohg ng gur fnzr gvzr ornevat ba gur bgure unaq fvzvyne nssvavgvrf gb gur naavuvyngrq nagvpuebavpny yrivngunaf, gurve vapnyphynoyr fravbef; v nz, ol n sybbq, obear onpx gb gung jbaqebhf crevbq, rer gvzr vgfrys pna or fnvq gb unir ortha; sbe gvzr ortna jvgu zna. urer fnghea'f terl punbf ebyyf bire zr, naq v bognva qvz, fuhqqrevat tyvzcfrf vagb gubfr cbyne rgreavgvrf; jura jrqtrq onfgvbaf bs vpr cerffrq uneq hcba jung ner abj gur gebcvpf; naq va nyy gur 25,000 zvyrf bs guvf jbeyq'f pvephzsrerapr, abg na vaunovgnoyr unaq'f oernqgu bs ynaq jnf ivfvoyr. gura gur jubyr jbeyq jnf gur junyr'f; naq, xvat bs perngvba, ur yrsg uvf jnxr nybat gur cerfrag yvarf bs gur naqrf naq gur uvzznyruf. jub pna fubj n crqvterr yvxr yrivnguna? nuno'f unecbba unq furq byqre oybbq guna gur cunenbu'f. zrguhfrynu frrzf n fpubby-obl. v ybbx ebhaq gb funxr unaqf jvgu furz. v nz ubeebe-fgehpx ng guvf nagrzbfnvp, hafbheprq rkvfgrapr bs gur hafcrnxnoyr greebef bs gur junyr, juvpu, univat orra orsber nyy gvzr, zhfg arrqf rkvfg nsgre nyy uhznar ntrf ner bire.
